## 🚀 Release Process

1. Merge feature branch into `main`
2. Run full test suite: `{{#eq packageManager "npm"}}npm run test{{else}}{{packageManager}} run test{{/eq}}`
3. Build: `{{#eq packageManager "npm"}}npm run build{{else}}{{packageManager}} run build{{/eq}}`
4. Tag release: `git tag v1.x.x`
5. Deploy to staging for validation
6. Deploy to production after approval

